FBIS4-10415 "drlat071__a94009" FBIS-LAT-94-071-A Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 ANNEX Brazil Senate Patents Bill Report To Be Ready 22 Apr Senate Patents Bill Report To Be Ready 22 Apr PY1304002994 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 12 Apr 94 Business and Economic Section p3--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY PY1304002994 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL Portuguese and Economic BFN [From the "Economic Report" column by Miriam Lage] [Text] Senator Jose Richa, the rapporteur of the patents draft law, on 11 April had lunch with Industry and Commerce Minister Elcio Alvares, who will be leaving for Geneva to sign the final terms of the Uruguay GATT Round. Richa informed Alvares that his report on the patents draft law will be ready by 22 April. After dispensing with further public hearings, the report will be submitted to the Senate Economic Committee. In one month, the Senate plenum could vote on the draft law.
